'''土卫六'''又稱為「'''[[泰坦|泰坦]]'''」（Titan），是环绕[[土星|土星]]运行的一颗[[天然卫星|卫星]]，是[[土星的卫星|土星卫星]]中最大的一个，也是[[太陽系|太陽系]][[太阳系天然卫星列表|第二大的衛星]]。[[荷兰|荷兰]][[物理学家|物理学家]]、[[天文学家|天文学家]]和[[数学家|数学家]][[克里斯蒂安·惠更斯|克里斯蒂安·惠更斯]]在1655年3月25日发现它，也是在太阳系内继[[木星|木星]][[伽利略卫星|伽利略卫星]]後发现的第一颗卫星。由於它是太陽系第一颗被发现擁有濃厚[[大氣層|大氣層]]的衞星，因此被高度懷疑有[[生命體|生命體]]的存在，科學家也推測大氣中的[[甲烷|甲烷]]可能是生命體的基礎。土衛六可以被視為一個時光機器，有助我們了解地球最初期的情況，揭開地球生物如何誕生之謎。

== 名称 ==
惠更斯简单的把这颗他发现的卫星称为「Saturni Luna」（土星的月球）。之後，[[乔瓦尼·多梅尼科·卡西尼|乔瓦尼·多梅尼科·卡西尼]]为了表达对[[法國|法國]]国王[[路易十四|路易十四]]的敬意将发现的四颗卫星：[[土卫三|土卫三]]（[[忒堤斯|忒堤斯]]），[[土卫四|土卫四]]（[[狄俄涅|狄俄涅]]），[[土卫五|土卫五]]（[[瑞亚|瑞亚]]），以及[[土卫八|土卫八]]（[[伊阿珀托斯|伊阿珀托斯]]）命名为「路易之星」（Sidera Lodoicea）。天文学家依据习惯把这五颗卫星以数字加以编号，其他的卫星则被称为「惠更斯卫星」或「土星的第六颗卫星」（以当时已知的各卫星距离土星的距離，由近至遠排列）。至於[[土卫一|土卫一]]（[[弥玛斯|弥玛斯]]）和[[土卫二|土卫二]]（[[恩賽勒達斯|恩賽勒達斯]]）則是在1789年被发现。

土卫六的英文名称「泰坦」和其他另外七颗当时已知的土星卫星的名称，都是由[[約翰·赫歇爾|約翰·赫歇爾]]爵士命名的（约翰·赫歇爾是[[威廉·赫歇爾|威廉·赫歇爾]]爵士之子，而威廉·赫歇爾是土卫一和土卫二的發現者）。约翰·赫歇爾在1847年出版的《在好望角天文观测的结果》（Results of Astronomical Observations Made at the Cape of Good Hope）<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://adsabs.harvard.edu//full/seri/MNRAS/0008//0000042.000.html |title=Observations of satellites of Saturn |accessdate=2005-01-09 |archive-date=2008-07-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080725063430/http://adsabs.harvard.edu//full/seri/MNRAS/0008//0000042.000.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>一书中把这颗新卫星命名为「泰坦」，提坦在神话中是[[克罗诺斯|克罗诺斯]]（他的[[罗马神话|罗马神话]]的对应者[[萨图尔努斯|萨图尔努斯]](或稱[[薩坦|薩坦]])为土星神）和他的兄弟姊妹们的统称。

== 物理特性 ==
土卫六是土星最大的卫星，也是太阳系第二大卫星，其体积甚至比行星[[水星|水星]]還大（虽然质量没有水星大），在太阳系的卫星中它的大小仅次于木星最大的卫星[[木卫三|木卫三]]。但最近的观测也显示其浓密的大气可能使人高估了它的直径。

土卫六平均半径2575公里，质量1.345×10<sup>23</sup>千克，平均密度1.880×10<sup>3</sup>千克/立方米。土卫六环绕土星[[公转|公转]]的轨道半长径为1,221,850公里，偏心率0.0292，轨道平面与土星赤道面的交角为0.33°，公转周期15天22时41分24秒。土卫六被土星[[潮汐鎖定|潮汐鎖定]]，其[[自转周期|自转周期]]与[[公转周期|公转周期]]相同。土卫六有浓密的大气，主要成分是[[氮|氮]]，表面大气压力1.5×10<sup>5</sup>[[帕斯卡|帕斯卡]]，表面温度-178°C。

土卫六质量与[[木卫三|木卫三]]、[[木卫四|木卫四]]、[[海卫一|海卫一]]與[[冥王星|冥王星]]大致类似。土卫六一半是[[冰|冰]]一半是固体材料。在多个不同结晶状冰层下方有直徑約3,400公里的固体核心，其内部应该因重力之故仍保持著炽热狀態。虽然土卫五以及其他的土星卫星也有类似的固體核心，但由於土衛六的体积巨大造成更強烈的重力压缩，而使得其核心密度較其他衛星高出許多。

==大气层==
{{main|土卫六大气层}}
[[File:Titan-Complex 'Anti-greenhouse'.jpg|thumb|right|upright|土卫六大气薄雾层真彩照片
]]
土卫六是已知唯一拥有突出[[大气层|大气层]]的卫星<ref name="NasaNews.moons">{{cite web |title=News Features: The Story of Saturn |url=http://saturn.jpl.nasa.gov/news/features/saturn-story/moons.cfm |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20051202030828/http://saturn.jpl.nasa.gov/news/features/saturn-story/moons.cfm |archive-date=December 2, 2005 |work=Cassini–Huygens Mission to Saturn & Titan |publisher=NASA & [[Jet_Propulsion_Lab|JPL]]|access-date=January 8, 2007 }}</ref>，也是[[太阳系|太阳系]]中除[[地球|地球]]外唯一富含[[氮|氮气]]的稠密大气层。卡西尼号在2004年对其进行的观测表明，土卫六是一个“[[大气层超旋转|超级旋转体]]”，就像[[金星|金星]]一样，其大气层旋转速度远快于表面<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.astrobio.net/news/article1480.html |title=Wind or Rain or Cold of Titan's Night? |date=March 11, 2005 |work=Astrobiology Magazine |archive-date=July 17, 2007 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070717081303/http://www.astrobio.net/news/article1480.html |access-date=August 24, 2007 }}</ref>。[[旅行者计划|旅行者号]]太空探测器的观测表明，土卫六大气层比地球的密度大，表面约为1.45个[[标准大气压|标准大气压]]，其质量大约是地球大气总质量的1.19倍，或者说是每表面面积质量的7.3倍。不透明的薄雾层阻挡了大部分来自太阳和其他光源的可见光，并模糊了土卫六的表面特征<ref name="Zubrin">{{cite book |last=Zubrin |first=Robert |title=Entering Space: Creating a Spacefaring Civilization |url=https://archive.org/details/enteringspacecre00zubr |url-access=registration |location=Section: Titan |pages=[https://archive.org/details/enteringspacecre00zubr/page/163 163–166] |publisher=Tarcher/Putnam |date=1999 |isbn=978-1-58542-036-0 }}</ref>。土卫六较低的重力意味着它的大气层比地球大气层向外延伸得更宽深<ref>{{cite magazine |title=Exploring the Surface of Titan with Cassini–Huygens |last=Turtle |first=Elizabeth P. |date=2007 |magazine=Smithsonian |url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cfCTmv-9GkE |access-date=April 18, 2009 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130720123340/http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cfCTmv-9GkE |archive-date=July 20, 2013}}</ref>。土卫六大气层在许多[[波长|波长]]上都不透明，因此，从轨道上无法获取完整的表面反射光谱<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Schröder |first1=S. E. |last2=Tomasko |first2=M. G. |last3=Keller |first3=H. U. |date=August 2005 |title=The reflectance spectrum of Titan's surface as determined by Huygens |page=726 |journal=American Astronomical Society, DPS Meeting No. 37, #46.15; Bulletin of the American Astronomical Society |volume=37 |issue=726 |bibcode=2005DPS....37.4615S}}</ref>，直到2004年[[卡西尼-惠更斯号|卡西尼-惠更斯号]]飞船抵达，才获得了第一张土卫六表面的直接图像<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.space.com/710-huygens-probe-sheds-light-titan.html |title=Huygens Probe Sheds New Light on Titan |last=de Selding |first=Petre |publisher=Space.com |date=January 21, 2005 |access-date=March 28, 2005 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121019133741/http://www.space.com/710-huygens-probe-sheds-light-titan.html |archive-date=October 19, 2012}}</ref>。

土卫六的大气成分由[[氮|氮]]（97%）、[[甲烷|甲烷]]（2.7±0.1%）、[[氢|氢]]（0.1–0.2%）和其他微量气体组成{{sfnp |Coustenis |Taylor |2008 |pp=154–155}}，还有微量的其他[[羟|碳氢化合物]]，如[[乙烷|乙烷]]、[[丁二炔|丁二炔]]、[[丙炔|丙炔]]、[[乙炔|乙炔]]和[[丙烷|丙烷]]以及[[氰基乙炔|氰基乙炔]]、[[氰化氢|氰化氢]]、[[二氧化碳|二氧化碳]]、[[一氧化碳|一氧化碳]]，[[氰|氰化物]]、[[氩|氩气]]和[[氦|氦气]]等<ref name="Niemann">{{cite journal |title=The abundances of constituents of Titan's atmosphere from the GCMS instrument on the Huygens probe |first1=H. B. |last1=Niemann |first2=S. K. |last2=Atreya |first3=S. J. |last3=Bauer |first4=G. R. |last4=Carignan |first5=J. E. |last5=Demick |first6=R. L. |last6=Frost |first7=D. |last7=Gautier |first8=J. A. |last8=Haberman |first9=D. N. |last9=Harpold |first10=D. M. |last10=Hunten |first11=G. |last11=Israel |first12=J. I. |last12=Lunine |first13=W. T. |last13=Kasprzak |first14=T. C. |last14=Owen |first15=M. |last15=Paulkovich |first16=F. |last16=Raulin |first17=E. |last17=Raaen |first18=S. H. |last18=Way | display-authors=1 |journal=Nature |volume=438 |pages=779–784 |date=2005 |doi=10.1038/nature04122 |pmid=16319830 |issue=7069 |bibcode=2005Natur.438..779N |url=https://deepblue.lib.umich.edu/bitstream/2027.42/62703/1/nature04122.pdf |hdl=2027.42/62703 |s2cid=4344046}}</ref>。这些碳氢化合物被认为形成于土卫六高层大气中，是[[甲烷|甲烷]]被太阳[[紫外线|紫外线]]分解所产生的反应，并产生了厚厚的橙色烟雾<ref name=waite>{{cite journal |last1=Waite |first1=J. H. |last2=Cravens |first2=T. E. |last3=Coates |first3=A. J. |last4=Crary |first4=F. J. |last5=Magee |first5=B. |last6=Westlake|first6=J. |date=2007 |title=The Process of Tholin Formation in Titan's Upper Atmosphere |journal=Science |volume=316 |doi=10.1126/science.1139727 |pmid=17495166 |issue=5826 |bibcode=2007Sci...316..870W |pages=870–5 |s2cid=25984655 }}</ref>。土卫六95%的时间都处在土星磁层内，这可能有助于保护它免受[[太阳风|太阳风]]的影响<ref>{{cite news |last=Courtland |first=Rachel |url=https://www.newscientist.com/article/dn14717-saturn-magnetises-its-moon-titan.html |title=Saturn magnetises its moon Titan |work=New Scientist |date=September 11, 2008 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150531045100/http://www.newscientist.com/article/dn14717-saturn-magnetises-its-moon-titan.html |archive-date=May 31, 2015 }}</ref>。

来自太阳的能量应能在5000万年内将土卫六大气中所有微量甲烷都转化为更复杂的碳氢化合物，这与太阳系年龄相比是很短暂的时间。这也表明甲烷必须由土卫六本身或其内部的储层来补充<ref>{{cite journal |title=Formation and evolution of Titan's atmosphere |last=Coustenis |first=A. |journal=Space Science Reviews |volume=116 |issue=1–2 |pages=171–184 |date=2005 |doi=10.1007/s11214-005-1954-2 |bibcode=2005SSRv..116..171C |s2cid=121298964 }}</ref>。大气层中甲烷的最终来源可能是它内部，通过[[冰火山|冰火山]]喷发释放出来的<ref name="NASA.sci.76">{{cite web |title=NASA Titan – Surface |publisher=NASA |url=http://saturn.jpl.nasa.gov/science/index.cfm?SciencePageID=76 |access-date=February 14, 2013 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130217182727/http://saturn.jpl.nasa.gov/science/index.cfm?SciencePageID=76 |archive-date=February 17, 2013 }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |title=Titan's methane cycle |first1=Sushil K. |last1=Atreyaa |first2=Elena Y. |last2=Adamsa |first3=Hasso B. |last3=Niemann |author4=Demick-Montelar, Jaime E. a|author5=Owen, Tobias C. |author6=Fulchignoni, Marcello |author7=Ferri, Francesca |author8=Wilson, Eric H. |date=2006 |doi=10.1016/j.pss.2006.05.028 |journal=Planetary and Space Science |volume=54 |issue=12 |pages=1177–1187 |bibcode=2006P&SS...54.1177A }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |journal=Nature |display-authors=8 |last=Stofan |first=E. R. |author2=Elachi, C.|author3=Lunine, J. I.|author4=Lorenz, R. D.|author5=Stiles, B.|author6=Mitchell, K. L.|author7=Ostro, S.|author8=Soderblom, L.|author9=Wood, C.|author10=Zebker, H.|author11=Wall, S.|author12=Janssen, M.|author13=Kirk, R.|author14=Lopes, R.|author15=Paganelli, F.|author16=Radebaugh, J.|author17=Wye, L.|author18=Anderson, Y.|author19=Allison, M.|author20=Boehmer, R.|author21=Callahan, P.|author22=Encrenaz, P.|author23=Flamini, E.|author24=Franscetti, G.|author25=Gim, Y.|author26=Hamilton, G.|author27=Hensley, S.|author28=Johnson, W. T. K.|author29=Kelleher, K.|author30=Muhleman, D.|author31=Paillou, P.|author32=Picardi, G.|author33=Posa, F.|author34=Roth, L.|author35=Seul, R.|author36=Shaffer, S.|author37=Vetrella, S.|author38=West, R. |volume=445 |date=2007 |doi=10.1038/nature05438 |pmid=17203056 |issue=7123 |title=The lakes of Titan |pages=61–64 |bibcode=2007Natur.445...61S |s2cid=4370622 }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |title=Episodic outgassing as the origin of atmospheric methane on Titan |last1=Tobie |first1=Gabriel |last2=Lunine |first2=Jonathan |last3=Sotin |first3=Cristophe |journal=Nature |volume=440 |issue=7080 |pages=61–64 |date=2006 |doi=10.1038/nature04497 |pmid=16511489 |bibcode=2006Natur.440...61T |title-link=atmospheric methane |s2cid=4335141 }}</ref>。
[[File:Titan-SaturnMoon-Maps-TraceGases-20141022.jpg|thumb]]中的[[稀有元素|微量]][[有机化合物|有机]]气体—[[异氢氰酸|异氢氰酸]]（左）和[[氰基乙炔|氰基乙炔]]（右）。]]
2013年4月3日，[[美国宇航局|美国宇航局]]根据对[[土卫六大气层|土卫六大气层]]的模拟研究，报告称土卫六上可能会出现复杂的[[有机化合物|有机化学物质]]，统称为[[托林_(天文学)|托林]]<ref name="PhysOrg-20130403" />。

2013年6月6日，安达卢西亚天体物理研究所（IAA-CSIC）的科学家报告在土卫六高层大气中检测到[[多环芳香烃|多环芳香烃]]<ref name="IAA-20130606">{{cite news |last=López-Puertas |first=Manuel |url=http://www.iaa.es/content/pahs-titans-upper-atmosphere |title=PAH's in Titan's Upper Atmosphere |date=June 6, 2013 |work=[[Spanish_National_Research_Council|CSIC]] |access-date=June 6, 2013 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131203030521/http://www.iaa.es/content/pahs-titans-upper-atmosphere |archive-date=December 3, 2013 }}</ref><ref name="#1">{{cite journal|arxiv=2001.02791|doi=10.1016/j.icarus.2019.113571|title=The 3.4μm absorption in Titan's stratosphere: Contribution of ethane, propane, butane and complex hydrogenated organics|journal=Icarus|volume=339|pages=113571|year=2020|last1=Cours|first1=T.|last2=Cordier|first2=D.|last3=Seignovert|first3=B.|last4=Maltagliati|first4=L.|last5=Biennier|first5=L.|bibcode=2020Icar..33913571C|s2cid=210116807}}</ref>。

2013年9月30日，[[美国宇航局|美国宇航局]]的卡西尼号探测器使用复合红外光谱仪（CIRS）在土卫六大气层中检测到了[[丙烯|丙烯]]<ref name="NASA-20130930">{{cite web |last1=Brown |first1=Dwayne |last2=Neal-Jones |first2=Nancy |last3=Zubritsky |first3=Elizabeth |last4=Cook |first4=Jia-Rui |title=NASA's Cassini Spacecraft Finds Ingredient of Household Plastic in Space |url=http://www.nasa.gov/content/goddard/nasas-cassini-spacecraft-finds-ingredient-of-household-plastic-in-space/ |date=September 30, 2013 |work=[[NASA|NASA]] |access-date=December 2, 2013 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131127041925/http://www.nasa.gov/content/goddard/nasas-cassini-spacecraft-finds-ingredient-of-household-plastic-in-space/ |archive-date=November 27, 2013}}</ref>，这是首次在地球以外的卫星或行星上发现的丙烯，也是红外光谱仪发现的第一种化学物质。丙烯的探测填补了一个神秘的观测空白，这一空白可以追溯到1980年美国宇航局[[旅行者1号|旅行者1号]]飞船第一次近距离飞越土卫六，期间发现构成土卫六棕色薄雾的许多气体是碳氢化合物，理论上形成于太阳紫外线[[光分解作用|光解]]甲烷所产生的自由基重组<ref name=waite/>。

2014年10月24日，在土卫六的极地云中发现了[[甲烷|甲烷]]<ref name="NASA-20141024-PD">{{cite web |last1=Dyches |first1=Preston |last2=Zubritsky |first2=Elizabeth |title=NASA Finds Methane Ice Cloud in Titan's Stratosphere |url=http://www.jpl.nasa.gov/news/news.php?feature=4354 |date=October 24, 2014 |work=[[NASA|NASA]] |access-date=October 31, 2014 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141028193849/http://www.jpl.nasa.gov/news/news.php?feature=4354 |archive-date=October 28, 2014}}</ref><ref name="NASA-20141024-EZ">{{cite web |last1=Zubritsky |first1=Elizabeth |last2=Dyches |first2=Preston |title=NASA Identifies Ice Cloud Above Cruising Altitude on Titan |url=http://www.nasa.gov/content/goddard/nasa-identifies-ice-cloud-above-cruising-altitude-on-titan |date=October 24, 2014 |work=[[NASA|NASA]] |access-date=October 31, 2014 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141031133440/http://www.nasa.gov/content/goddard/nasa-identifies-ice-cloud-above-cruising-altitude-on-titan/ |archive-date=October 31, 2014}}</ref>。

{{wide image|Titan-Earth-PolarClouds-20141024.jpg|600px|align-cap=center|土卫六上由甲烷构成的[[极地平流层云|极地云]]（左）与[[地球|地球]]上水或水冰构成的极地云（右）对比。}}

== 氣候 ==
{{main|土衛六的氣候}}
[[File:Vortex_on_saturn's_moon_titan.png|thumb]] |text-top]]
土卫六表面温度约为 94 K（-179.2 °C），在这种气温下，水冰的[[蒸气压|蒸气压]]极低，因此所存在的少量[[水蒸气|水蒸气]]似乎仅限于[[平流层|平流层]]中<ref name="CottiniNixon2012">{{cite journal |display-authors=8 |last1=Cottini |first1=V. |last2=Nixon |first2=C.A. |last3=Jennings |first3=D.E. |last4=Anderson |first4=C.M. |last5=Gorius |first5=N. |last6=Bjoraker |first6=G.L. |last7=Coustenis |first7=A. |last8=Teanby |first8=N.A. |last9=Achterberg |first9=R.K. |last10=Bézard |first10=B. |last11=de Kok |first11=R. |last12=Lellouch |first12=E. |last13=Irwin |first13=P.G.J. |last14=Flasar |first14=F.M. |last15=Bampasidis |first15=G. |title=Water vapor in Titan's stratosphere from Cassini CIRS far-infrared spectra |journal=Icarus |volume=220 |issue=2 |date=2012 |pages=855–862 |issn=0019-1035 |doi=10.1016/j.icarus.2012.06.014 |bibcode = 2012Icar..220..855C |hdl=2060/20120013575|hdl-access=free }}</ref>。土卫六接收到的太阳光大约只有地球的1%<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.space.com/7103-titan-world-earth.html |title=Titan: A World Much Like Earth |publisher=Space.com |date=August 6, 2009 |access-date=April 2, 2012|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121012005030/http://www.space.com/7103-titan-world-earth.html |archive-date=October 12, 2012 }}</ref>，并且在抵达地表之前，大约有90%的阳光被厚厚的大气层吸收，最后只剩0.1%的阳光到达了地表<ref>[https://arstechnica.com/science/2012/01/like-ogres-titans-atmosphere-may-have-layers/ Faint sunlight enough to drive weather, clouds on Saturn’s moon Titan] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170403194843/https://arstechnica.com/science/2012/01/like-ogres-titans-atmosphere-may-have-layers/ |date=April 3, 2017 }} Between the large distance from the Sun and the thick atmosphere, Titan's surface receives about 0.1 percent of the solar energy that Earth does.</ref>。

大气中的[[甲烷|甲烷]]会在土卫六表面产生[[温室效应|温室效应]]，否则土卫六会更寒冷<ref name="oil">{{cite web |url=http://www.space.com/4968-titan-oil-earth.html |title=Titan Has More Oil Than Earth |date=February 13, 2008 |access-date=February 13, 2008|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120708055735/http://www.space.com/4968-titan-oil-earth.html |archive-date=July 8, 2012 }}</ref>。另一种相反的情况则是：土卫六大气中的[[霾|雾霾]]会将阳光反射回太空，从而产生[[反温室效应|反温室效应]]，抵消了部分温室效应，使其表面较上层大气明显变冷。<ref>{{cite journal |doi=10.1126/science.11538492 |first1=C.P. |last1=McKay |first2=J. B. |last2=Pollack |first3=R. |last3=Courtin |date=1991 |title=The greenhouse and antigreenhouse effects on Titan |journal=Science |volume=253 |issue=5024 |pages=1118–1121 |pmid=11538492 |url=http://pdfs.semanticscholar.org/55b1/69bd4d31772da8c5e7ad17586baff4389481.pdf |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200412143944/http://pdfs.semanticscholar.org/55b1/69bd4d31772da8c5e7ad17586baff4389481.pdf|archive-date=2020-04-12 |bibcode=1991Sci...253.1118M |s2cid=10384331 }}</ref>
[[File:PIA18420-Titan-MethaneClouds-20140722.gif|thumb]] |access-date=August 13, 2014|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140813004912/http://www.jpl.nasa.gov/news/news.php?release=2014-274 |archive-date=August 13, 2014 }}</ref>。]]
土卫六的云层可能由[[甲烷|甲烷]]、[[乙烷|乙烷]]或其他简单[[有机物|有机物]]组成，这些云层分散而多变，不时笼罩着阴霾<ref name="nineplanets" />。惠更斯探测器的发现表明，土卫六大气层周期性地将液态甲烷和其他[[有机化合物|有机化合物]]通过降雨回落到其表面<ref name="planetary-Arizona_Icebox">{{cite news |url=http://planetary.org/news/2005/0121_Titan_Arizona_in_an_Icebox.html |title=Titan: Arizona in an Icebox? |last=Lakdawalla |first=Emily |author-link=Emily Lakdawalla |publisher=The Planetary Society |date=January 21, 2004 |archive-date=February 12, 2010 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100212062535/http://planetary.org/news/2005/0121_Titan_Arizona_in_an_Icebox.html |access-date=March 28, 2005 }}</ref>。

云层通常覆盖了1%的土卫六球面，不过也观察到一些爆发事件，使云层覆盖率迅速扩大至8%。一种假说认为，南方云层是在夏季日照增强，导致大气抬升产生[[对流|对流]]时形成的。这种解释较为勉强，事实上在土卫六南方，不仅[[夏至|夏至]]之后，在[[仲春|仲春]]时节也观察到了云气的形成。南极甲烷湿度的增加可能是造成云量迅速增多的原因<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Emily L. |first1=Schaller |last2=Brouwn |first2=Michael E. |last3=Roe |first3=Henry G. |last4=Bouchez |first4=Antonin H. |date=2006 |title=A large cloud outburst at Titan's south pole |doi=10.1016/j.icarus.2005.12.021 |journal=Icarus |issue=1 |pages=224–229 |url=http://www.gps.caltech.edu/~mbrown/papers/ps/largecloud.pdf |volume=182 |bibcode=2006Icar..182..224S |access-date=August 23, 2007|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070926102541/http://www.gps.caltech.edu/~mbrown/papers/ps/largecloud.pdf |archive-date=2007-09-26}}</ref>。直到2010年，土卫六南半球还处于夏季之中。在此之后，影响土卫六运行的土星轨道才将土卫六北半球移至到阳光下<ref name="Titan wind">{{cite news|title=The Way the Wind Blows on Titan |date=June 1, 2007 |url=http://saturn.jpl.nasa.gov/news/cassinifeatures/feature20070601f/ |access-date=June 2, 2007 |publisher=Jet Propulsion Laboratory|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090427110242/http://saturn.jpl.nasa.gov/news/cassinifeatures/feature20070601f/ |archive-date=April 27, 2009 }}</ref>。预计季节转换后，乙烷将会开始在南极上空凝结<ref>{{cite journal |title=Huge ethane cloud discovered on Titan |last=Shiga |first=David |journal=New Scientist |volume=313 |page=1620 |date=2006 |url=https://www.newscientist.com/article/dn10073-huge-ethane-cloud-discovered-on-titan.html |access-date=August 7, 2007|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081220030748/http://www.newscientist.com/article/dn10073-huge-ethane-cloud-discovered-on-titan.html |archive-date=December 20, 2008 }}</ref>。

==表面特征==
{{See also|土卫六表面特征列表}}
[[File:First_global_geologic_map_of_Titan_(PIA23174).jpg|thumb]]
<gallery mode="packed" heights="140px">
PIA20713-Titan-SaturnMoon-LabeledFeaturesIAU-June2015.jpg|附[[国际天文联合会|国际天文联合会]]标注的土卫六全球地图（2016年8月）。
PIA21923-Titan-SaturnMoon-InfraredViews-20180718.jpg|红外光下的土卫六视图（2004年–2017年）
PIA19657-SaturnMoon-Titan-NorthPole-20140407.jpg|土卫六北极 (2014年)
PIA19657-SaturnMoon-Titan-SouthPole-20140407.jpg|土卫六南极 (2014年)
</gallery>
土卫六的表面被描述为“复杂、流体作用和地质年轻<ref>{{cite journal |last=Mahaffy |first=Paul R. |date=May 13, 2005 |title=Intensive Titan Exploration Begins |journal=[[Science_(magazine)|Science]] |volume=308 |issue=5724 |pages=969–970 |doi=10.1126/science.1113205 |pmid=15890870 |bibcode=2005Sci...308..969M |citeseerx=10.1.1.668.2877 |s2cid=41758337}}</ref>。土卫六自从太阳系形成以来就一直存在，但它的表面要年轻得多，在1亿到10亿年之间，地质活动可能已重塑了土卫六的表面<ref name="puzzling geologic">{{cite web |url=http://web.mit.edu/newsoffice/2012/river-networks-on-titan-0720.html |title=River networks on Titan point to a puzzling geologic history |first=Jennifer |last=Chu |date=July 2012 |publisher=MIT Research |access-date=July 24, 2012|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121030175726/http://web.mit.edu/newsoffice/2012/river-networks-on-titan-0720.html |archive-date=October 30, 2012 }}</ref>。土卫六大气层厚度是地球的四倍<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.nasa.gov/feature/goddard/2020/nasa-scientists-discover-a-weird-molecule-in-titan-s-atmosphere |title='Weird' Molecule Discovered in Titan's Atmosphere - nasa.gov |access-date=2021-07-26 |archive-date=2021-07-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210715113442/https://www.nasa.gov/feature/goddard/2020/nasa-scientists-discover-a-weird-molecule-in-titan-s-atmosphere/ }}</ref>，这使得天文仪器很难以用可见光成像其表面<ref>{{cite news |first=Taimoor |last=Tariq |title=Titan, Saturn's largest moon is finally unravelled in detail |date=March 12, 2012 |url=http://www.newspakistan.pk/2012/03/12/Titan-Saturn-s-largest-moon-is-finally-unravelled-in-detail/ |work=News Pakistan |access-date=March 12, 2012|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140811000259/http://www.newspakistan.pk/2012/03/12/Titan-Saturn-s-largest-moon-is-finally-unravelled-in-detail/ |archive-date=August 11, 2014}}</ref>。卡西尼号探测器使用红外光谱、雷达测高仪和[[合成孔径雷达|合成孔径雷达]]成像在近距飞越时绘制了部分土卫六地图。首批图像揭示了不同的地质情况，包括粗糙和平坦的区域。有些地貌可能起源于将水-氨混合物排放到地表的[[冰火山|冰火山活动]]。也有证据表明土卫六的冰壳可能相当坚硬<ref name="Hemingway et al. 2013" /><ref name="jpl.nasa.gov" />，这意味着很少有地质活动<ref name="Moore and Pappalardo 2011">{{Cite journal| doi = 10.1016/j.icarus.2011.01.019| title = Titan: An exogenic world?| journal = Icarus| volume = 212| issue = 2| pages = 790–806| year = 2011| last1 = Moore| first1 = J. M.| last2 = Pappalardo| first2 = R. T.| bibcode = 2011Icar..212..790M| url = https://zenodo.org/record/1259045| access-date = 2021-07-26| archive-date = 2021-07-26| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210726123209/https://zenodo.org/record/1259045}}</ref>。

[[File:PIA18309-SaturnMoonTitan-SenkyoRegion-20150108.jpg|thumb]]]]

还有一些条纹状的特征，其中一些长达数百公里，似乎是由风吹颗粒所形成的<ref>{{cite magazine |last=Battersby |first=Stephen |date=October 29, 2004 |title=Titan's complex and strange world revealed |magazine=[[New_Scientist|New Scientist]] |url=https://www.newscientist.com/article/dn6598 |access-date=August 31, 2007 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081221052236/http://www.newscientist.com/article/dn6598 |archive-date=December 21, 2008 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://saturn.jpl.nasa.gov/spacecraft/overview/ |title=Spacecraft: Cassini Orbiter Instruments, RADAR |work=Cassini–Huygens Mission to Saturn & Titan |publisher=NASA, Jet Propulsion Laboratory |access-date=August 31, 2007|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110807011916/http://saturn.jpl.nasa.gov/spacecraft/overview/ |archive-date=August 7, 2011}}</ref>。检测还表明地表相对平坦，少数看上去像撞击坑的结构似乎已被填平，也许是由于碳氢化合物或火山造成的降雨所致。雷达测高显示土卫六表面高度变化很小，通常不超过150米。偶尔会发现500米的海拔变化，土卫六上的山脉一般高几百米至1公里以上<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Lorenz |first1=R. D. |last2=Callahan |first2=P. S. |last3=Gim |first3=Y. |last4=Alberti |first4=G. |last5=Flamini |first5=E. |last6=Seu |first6=R. |last7=Picardi |first7=G. |last8=Orosei |first8=R. |last9=Zebker |first9=H. |last10=Lunine |first10=J. |last11=Hamilton |first11=G. |last12=Hensley |first12=S. |last13=Johnson |first13=W. T. K. |last14=Schaffer |first14=S. |last15=Wall |first15=S. |last16=West |first16=R. |last17=Francescetti |first17=G. |display-authors=1 |date=2007 |title=Titan's Shape, Radius and Landscape from Cassini Radar Altimetry |journal=Lunar and Planetary Science Conference |volume=38 |issue=1338 |url=http://www.lpi.usra.edu/meetings/lpsc2007/pdf/1329.pdf |bibcode=2007LPI....38.1329L |page=1329 |access-date=August 27, 2007 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070926102540/http://www.lpi.usra.edu/meetings/lpsc2007/pdf/1329.pdf |archive-date=September 26, 2007 }}</ref>。

土卫六的表面有明亮和黑暗的广阔区域，其中包括[[上都_(土卫六)|上都区]]，一处辽阔的赤道[[反射_(物理学)|反射]]区，面积约[[澳大利亚|澳洲]]般大小。1994年，它先是在[[哈勃空间望远镜|哈勃空间望远镜]]拍摄的[[红外线|红外线]]照片中被发现，后又被卡西尼号探测器观测到。这片蜿蜒的区域布满了丘陵，被山谷和裂峡切开<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.sciencedaily.com/releases/2006/07/060721202957.htm |title=Cassini Reveals Titan's Xanadu Region To Be An Earth-Like Land |date=July 23, 2006 |website=Science Daily |access-date=August 27, 2007 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110629211805/http://www.sciencedaily.com/releases/2006/07/060721202957.htm |archive-date=June 29, 2011}}</ref>。某些地方纵横交织着黑色的线性-弯曲的地形特征，类似于山脊或裂缝，这些可能代表了[[地质构造|构造]]活动，表明上都区在地质上是年轻的。或者，这些线性构造可能是液体形成的水道，表明古老的地形已经被河流系统所分割<ref>{{cite journal |display-authors=8 |last1=Barnes |first1=Jason W. |last2=Brown |first2=Robert H. |last3=Soderblom |first3=Laurence |last4=Buratti |first4=Bonnie J. |last5=Sotin |first5=Christophe |last6=Rodriguez |first6=Sebastien |last7=Le Mouèlic |first7=Stephane |last8=Baines |first8=Kevin H. |last9=Clark |first9=Roger |last10=Nicholson |first10=Phil |date=2006 |title=Global-scale surface spectral variations on Titan seen from Cassini/VIMS |doi=10.1016/j.icarus.2006.08.021 |journal=Icarus |issue=1 |volume=186 |url=http://c3po.barnesos.net/publications/papers/Titan.spectral.diversity.pdf |archive-date=July 25, 2011 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110725155935/http://c3po.barnesos.net/publications/papers/Titan.spectral.diversity.pdf |access-date=August 27, 2007 |pages=242–258 |bibcode=2007Icar..186..242B }}</ref>。从地球表面和卡西尼号上观察到，土卫六上其他地方都有类似大小的黑暗区域，其中至少有一处，土卫六上的第二大海洋，[[丽姬亚海|丽姬亚海]]几乎是一座纯净的[[甲烷|甲烷]]海洋<ref name="methane sea">{{cite news |last=Klotz |first=Irene |url=http://www.space.com/32741-one-of-titans-strange-seas-is-nearly-pure-methane.html |title=One of Titan |work=Discovery News |publisher=Space.com |date=April 28, 2016 |access-date=May 1, 2016 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160430113237/http://www.space.com/32741-one-of-titans-strange-seas-is-nearly-pure-methane.html |archive-date=2016-04-30}}</ref><ref name="Le Gall 2016">{{cite journal |title=Composition, seasonal change, and bathymetry of Ligeia Mare, Titan, derived from its microwave thermal emission |journal=Journal of Geophysical Research |date=February 25, 2016 |last1=Le Gall |first1=A. |last2=Malaska |first2=M. J. |doi=10.1002/2015JE004920 |bibcode=2016JGRE..121..233L |display-authors=etal |volume=121 |issue=2 |pages=233–251   |url=https://hal.archives-ouvertes.fr/hal-01259869/file/Le_Gall_2016_Composition%2C.pdf |doi-access=free |access-date=2021-07-26 |archive-date=2021-07-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210726123200/https://hal.archives-ouvertes.fr/hal-01259869/file/Le_Gall_2016_Composition,.pdf }}</ref>。

